{"key":"processedPost-13675528","value":{"id":13675528,"first":13675273,"last":13679706,"when":1293132840,"utime":"12/23/10 09:34 PM","content":"<blockquote>Quote:<br /><strong>mycobeginner said:</strong><br />how else can i measure 5gs of agar and lme?</blockquote><br />If you're in the US, a nickel weighs five grams.&nbsp; Place a nickel at one end of a ruler and your agar powder at the other end.&nbsp; Balance it in the middle on a pencil or cig lighter, etc.&nbsp; When it's balanced, your powder is 5 grams. <img style=\"max-width:192px;height:auto;\" src=\"https://files.shroomery.org/smileys/shrug.gif\" alt=\":shrug:\" title=\":shrug:\"/><br />RR","title":"Re: agar qestion"}}